ossc.notes: These equinox binaries are from the current stream for the ongoing 4.6.3+ Equinox (Neon.3+). The 4.6.3+ Equinox is in the R4_6_maintenance branch which IES can produce supported patch builds from. A separate OSSC approval needs to be done on these binaries until IES can produce the supported patch and made available from the IBM Eclipse SDK (IES) download site and is on the All Usage Approved (AUA) list.
